		<p>
			<font face="verdana" size="3" color="#9f3215"><b>    Siela's Newworld Guide to Baking</b></font>
			<br>
			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="#9f3215">
			<b><A href="mailto:Zoomoes@hotmail.com">Siela |GNM-WIZ-Fennin Ro|</a> | 
